00:14:26.740 --> 00:14:28.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pee and poop.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:14:28.660 --> 00:14:29.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And weakness.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:14:30.080 --> 00:14:32.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- Because I'm the big brother.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:14:32.960 --> 00:14:34.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If there's something I
can do about it,</b></Default>

c0000331
00:14:34.460 --> 00:14:35.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanna do it.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:14:35.710 --> 00:14:37.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

c0000333
00:14:37.750 --> 00:14:39.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But there's nothing I
can do about this.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:14:40.380 --> 00:14:41.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:14:42.220 --> 00:14:44.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, geez, I'm such an idiot!
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000336
00:14:45.010 --> 00:14:46.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big sis didn't say anything
about it 'cause there</b></Default>

c0000337
00:14:46.720 --> 00:14:47.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was nothing we could do.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:14:48.050 --> 00:14:49.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm seriously sorry.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:14:49.720 --> 00:14:51.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell chimes]</b></Default>

c0000340
00:14:52.310 --> 00:14:54.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> - Hi, I'm the school counselor,
Tomobe.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:14:55.310 --> 00:14:58.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To start, it can be as simple
as walking along the route</b></Default>

c0000342
00:14:58.150 --> 00:15:00.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to school for just a little bit.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:15:00.440 --> 00:15:02.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once there, it's okay to go
to the nurse's office</b></Default>

c0000344
00:15:03.030 --> 00:15:04.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>instead of to class.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:15:04.280 --> 00:15:05.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- W--would the nurse's
office count</b></Default>

c0000346
00:15:05.990 --> 00:15:07.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as going to school, though?</b></Default>

c0000347
00:15:07.410 --> 00:15:09.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, it absolutely would.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:15:09.410 --> 00:15:11.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But that's still different
from everyone else, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000349
00:15:11.660 --> 00:15:13.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, perhaps.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:15:13.120 --> 00:15:14.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But even if they all seem
the same,</b></Default>

c0000351
00:15:15.000 --> 00:15:17.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everyone has something
that makes them different.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:15:17.420 --> 00:15:19.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For instance,
some kids are taller,</b></Default>

c0000353
00:15:19.380 --> 00:15:20.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and some kids are shorter.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:15:20.800 --> 00:15:22.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Some kids are good at running</b></Default>

c0000355
00:15:22.300 --> 00:15:24.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and some aren't very athletic
at all.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:15:24.260 --> 00:15:26.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Each individual person
has their own pace.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:15:27.010 --> 00:15:29.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why whatever result comes
from you putting</b></Default>

c0000358
00:15:29.760 --> 00:15:33.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in your best effort definitely
counts as you going to school.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:15:33.180 --> 00:15:35.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Th--then even if it's just
to the nurse's office,</b></Default>

c0000360
00:15:35.730 --> 00:15:37.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can circle it?
- Circle?</b></Default>

c0000361
00:15:37.730 --> 00:15:39.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, oh this.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:15:41.360 --> 00:15:43.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [giggles]
I think you should.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:15:43.690 --> 00:15:46.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I--if that's the case then
Kaede would most definitely like</b></Default>

c0000364
00:15:46.490 --> 00:15:47.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to go to school.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:15:47.740 --> 00:15:50.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000366
00:15:50.780 --> 00:15:53.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[melancholic music]</b></Default>

c0000367
00:15:53.740 --> 00:15:54.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000368
00:15:54.910 --> 00:15:58.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales and exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000369
00:15:59.630 --> 00:16:00.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000370
00:16:00.750 --> 00:16:07.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000371
00:16:09.050 --> 00:16:10.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000372
00:16:13.560 --> 00:16:14.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[girls giggling]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000373
00:16:14.720 --> 00:16:16.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000374
00:16:16.140 --> 00:16:18.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're kidding me!
- It's true. I swear.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:16:18.850 --> 00:16:20.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what do you think
she said after that?</b></Default>

c0000376
00:16:20.400 --> 00:16:21.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What?</b></Default>

c0000377
00:16:21.810 --> 00:16:23.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- They're not laughing
about you, Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:16:23.900 --> 00:16:24.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's nothing to worry about.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:16:25.070 --> 00:16:26.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you sure?</b></Default>

c0000380
00:16:26.610 --> 00:16:28.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you think making people
laugh is that easy to do,</b></Default>

c0000381
00:16:28.910 --> 00:16:30.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're sorely mistaken.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:16:30.280 --> 00:16:32.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Th--the path of a comedian
is a steep one.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:16:34.410 --> 00:16:36.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We tried plenty hard
for today.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:16:36.540 --> 00:16:38.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go back
and eat some pudi--</b></Default>

c0000385
00:16:39.960 --> 00:16:41.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000386
00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:47.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede is determined to make
it all the way to school today.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:16:47.590 --> 00:16:49.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's got this.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:16:49.090 --> 00:16:51.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Take your time.
No need to be so impatient.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:16:51.090 --> 00:16:53.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- K--Kaede's not impatient!</b></Default>

c0000390
00:16:53.260 --> 00:16:55.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Even Ms. Tomobe said you
can take it slow, didn't she?</b></Default>

c0000391
00:16:55.890 --> 00:16:57.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000392
00:16:58.600 --> 00:17:00.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's wrong?</b></Default>

c0000393
00:17:00.230 --> 00:17:01.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's not good enough
for Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:17:02.060 --> 00:17:03.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you mean?</b></Default>

c0000395
00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:05.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000396
00:17:07.610 --> 00:17:11.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede, let's take a break
from practicing today, okay?</b></Default>

c0000397
00:17:11.910 --> 00:17:13.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [breathing heavily]
- Kaede!</b></Default>

c0000398
00:17:13.910 --> 00:17:16.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [panicked breathing]</b></Default>

c0000399
00:17:18.290 --> 00:17:19.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede!
- [gasping]</b></Default>

c0000400
00:17:19.660 --> 00:17:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's okay to take it slow!</b></Default>

c0000401
00:17:21.080 --> 00:17:23.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But it's not, though!
You don't get it!</b></Default>

c0000402
00:17:23.500 --> 00:17:25.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede doesn't have the time
to be taking it slow!</b></Default>

c0000403
00:17:25.750 --> 00:17:28.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- [breathing erratically]</b></Default>

c0000404
00:17:28.130 --> 00:17:31.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hold on.
Does she know about that?</b></Default>

c0000405
00:17:31.180 --> 00:17:34.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[tense music]</b></Default>

c0000406
00:17:34.180 --> 00:17:37.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000407
00:17:38.020 --> 00:17:39.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[girls laughing]
[both gasping]</b></Default>

c0000408
00:17:40.020 --> 00:17:42.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What is up with that?
- I know. Hilarious.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:17:42.810 --> 00:17:44.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000410
00:17:45.060 --> 00:17:47.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why? Why?</b></Default>

c0000411
00:17:47.730 --> 00:17:49.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:17:49.740 --> 00:17:51.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [crying]</b></Default>

c0000413
00:17:51.400 --> 00:17:53.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why won't you let Kaede go?</b></Default>

c0000414
00:17:53.410 --> 00:17:55.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede wants to go to school.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:17:55.320 --> 00:17:57.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why won't her legs move like
they're supposed to?</b></Default>

c0000416
00:17:57.290 --> 00:17:58.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:17:58.580 --> 00:18:00.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede will not go home!</b></Default>

c0000418
00:18:00.660 --> 00:18:02.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She won't go home!</b></Default>

c0000419
00:18:02.250 --> 00:18:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until she can make it to school,</b></Default>

c0000420
00:18:03.580 --> 00:18:05.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she'll keep on trying!</b></Default>

c0000421
00:18:05.250 --> 00:18:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'll keep practicing!
[crying]</b></Default>

c0000422
00:18:08.340 --> 00:18:10.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- All right.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:18:10.260 --> 00:18:12.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'll make sure you getting
to school becomes a reality.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:18:12.970 --> 00:18:16.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? You really mean it?
- Yes, I do.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:18:16.140 --> 00:18:18.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But before we continue
with our practice,</b></Default>

c0000426
00:18:18.100 --> 00:18:19.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're going to take
a little break.</b></Default>

c0000427
00:18:19.430 --> 00:18:21.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We're taking a break?</b></Default>

c0000428
00:18:21.140 --> 00:18:23.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We are. At the best place
I can think of.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:18:24.150 --> 00:18:27.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000430
00:18:29.190 --> 00:18:30.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There's a lot of people here.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:18:31.030 --> 00:18:33.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If this amount is enough
to scare you off,</b></Default>

c0000432
00:18:33.110 --> 00:18:34.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'll never make it to school.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:18:34.410 --> 00:18:36.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- R--right.
I'll push through.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:18:39.540 --> 00:18:43.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>B--big brother, where's this
best place you talked about?</b></Default>

c0000435
00:18:43.210 --> 00:18:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't worry, 'kay?
Almost there.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:18:45.330 --> 00:18:46.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[beeps]</b></Default>

c0000437
00:18:48.130 --> 00:18:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother,
are we there yet?</b></Default>

c0000438
00:18:50.170 --> 00:18:51.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Almost.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:18:55.300 --> 00:18:56.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We're here.
Take a look.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:18:59.180 --> 00:19:00.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000441
00:19:00.600 --> 00:19:03.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the zoo!
We came to the zoo, big brother!</b></Default>

c0000442
00:19:04.020 --> 00:19:05.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well I told you it
was the best place</b></Default>

c0000443
00:19:05.480 --> 00:19:06.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could think of, didn't I?</b></Default>

c0000444
00:19:07.400 --> 00:19:09.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Enjoy your time.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:19:09.440 --> 00:19:11.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Smells like Nasuno
before getting a bath.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:19:12.030 --> 00:19:13.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No mistaking the smell
of animals.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:19:13.940 --> 00:19:15.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
Pandas!</b></Default>

c0000448
00:19:15.950 --> 00:19:17.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look, big brother!
The pandas!</b></Default>

c0000449
00:19:17.870 --> 00:19:19.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The pandas are right over there!
- [gasping]</b></Default>

c0000450
00:19:19.870 --> 00:19:21.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Look at them!</b></Default>

c0000451
00:19:21.200 --> 00:19:24.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That one's walking around!
- It sure is.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:19:24.160 --> 00:19:25.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And that panda over there
is eating!</b></Default>

c0000453
00:19:26.040 --> 00:19:27.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It sure is.</b></Default>

c0000454
00:19:27.210 --> 00:19:28.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Pandas are so big!</b></Default>

c0000455
00:19:28.710 --> 00:19:30.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- They are called giant pandas.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:19:30.290 --> 00:19:32.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
It's looking at us!</b></Default>

c0000457
00:19:33.260 --> 00:19:35.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, never mind.
It went back to eating again.</b></Default>

c0000458
00:19:36.050 --> 00:19:38.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Bamboo isn't very
nutrient-dense which means</b></Default>

c0000459
00:19:38.800 --> 00:19:40.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>pandas need to spend
the majority of the day eating</b></Default>

c0000460
00:19:40.970 --> 00:19:42.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as much as they can just
to survive.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:19:42.770 --> 00:19:44.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least that's what
I heard on TV.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:19:44.680 --> 00:19:46.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Life is tough for pandas, too.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:19:47.020 --> 00:19:49.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Everyone's doing their best
to live their lives, huh?</b></Default>

c0000464
00:19:50.110 --> 00:19:52.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[melancholic music]</b></Default>

c0000465
00:19:53.070 --> 00:19:59.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000466
00:20:04.370 --> 00:20:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother,
it's a lesser panda!</b></Default>

c0000467
00:20:06.330 --> 00:20:07.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It is lesser.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:20:07.870 --> 00:20:10.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's so small.
- Well, they are lesser.</b></Default>

c0000469
00:20:10.130 --> 00:20:11.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's so adorable!</b></Default>

c0000470
00:20:13.590 --> 00:20:15.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede really loves pandas
after all.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:20:15.920 --> 00:20:18.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It feels a little sad
to say goodbye to them.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:20:18.260 --> 00:20:19.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You can just
come back again later.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:20:19.760 --> 00:20:21.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But Kaede is...</b></Default>

c0000474
00:20:22.850 --> 00:20:23.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000475
00:20:25.640 --> 00:20:27.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look. It's an annual pass.</b></Default>

c0000476
00:20:27.850 --> 00:20:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it's all yours.</b></Default>

c0000477
00:20:29.150 --> 00:20:30.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000478
00:20:30.980 --> 00:20:32.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- With this you could come back
and see the pandas every day</b></Default>

c0000479
00:20:32.940 --> 00:20:33.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you wanted to.</b></Default>

c0000480
00:20:33.940 --> 00:20:35.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's amazing!</b></Default>

c0000481
00:20:35.530 --> 00:20:37.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the big brotherest
big brother there is!</b></Default>

c0000482
00:20:37.610 --> 00:20:40.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it okay for Kaede
to come back and visit again?</b></Default>

c0000483
00:20:40.160 --> 00:20:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Of course.
What a silly question.</b></Default>

c0000484
00:20:41.950 --> 00:20:43.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I made a point to get
the annual pass</b></Default>

c0000485
00:20:43.990 --> 00:20:45.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so it'd be a waste of money not
to visit a bunch.</b></Default>

c0000486
00:20:47.830 --> 00:20:49.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede would like that.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:20:49.290 --> 00:20:51.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To come back a bunch
and get our money's worth.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:20:51.880 --> 00:20:52.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000489
00:20:57.840 --> 00:20:58.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000490
00:21:00.840 --> 00:21:01.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000491
00:21:05.010 --> 00:21:06.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede was even able
to go shopping!</b></Default>

c0000492
00:21:07.060 --> 00:21:08.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Want me to hold it?</b></Default>

c0000493
00:21:08.100 --> 00:21:09.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede purchased this pudding</b></Default>

c0000494
00:21:09.600 --> 00:21:11.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so Kaede will carry it herself.</b></Default>

c0000495
00:21:13.270 --> 00:21:16.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Big brother, our apartment
is that way, right?</b></Default>

c0000496
00:21:16.440 --> 00:21:18.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There's a shortcut
if we go this way.</b></Default>

c0000497
00:21:29.500 --> 00:21:31.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede had no idea there
was a shortcut.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:21:31.870 --> 00:21:33.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, you're still
an amateur when</b></Default>

c0000499
00:21:33.210 --> 00:21:34.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it comes to roads around here.</b></Default>

c0000500
00:21:34.670 --> 00:21:36.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Does that make you
a seasoned veteran, big brother?</b></Default>

c0000501
00:21:36.880 --> 00:21:38.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You could call me a pro.</b></Default>

c0000502
00:21:38.510 --> 00:21:39.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wow!</b></Default>

c0000503
00:21:39.920 --> 00:21:41.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000504
00:21:43.430 --> 00:21:45.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
Big brother, this--</b></Default>

c0000505
00:21:45.600 --> 00:21:47.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>m--my middle school!</b></Default>

c0000506
00:21:47.390 --> 00:21:49.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's late now so keep
the volume down.</b></Default>

c0000507
00:21:50.560 --> 00:21:52.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There.
- You shouldn't do that,</b></Default>

c0000508
00:21:52.480 --> 00:21:53.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>big brother!
- Come on.</b></Default>

c0000509
00:21:53.850 --> 00:21:54.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But it's--</b></Default>

c0000510
00:21:54.940 --> 00:21:55.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We're only gonna sneak</b></Default>

c0000511
00:21:55.940 --> 00:21:56.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a little peak real quick.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:21:58.150 --> 00:22:00.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- J--just a little, okay?</b></Default>

c0000513
00:22:03.700 --> 00:22:05.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
- I guess this</b></Default>

c0000514
00:22:05.320 --> 00:22:06.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is your first trip
to your school.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:22:09.700 --> 00:22:12.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, looks like this
is class 3-1.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:22:12.160 --> 00:22:14.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is this the room where Kaede
will be taking her classes?</b></Default>

c0000517
00:22:24.340 --> 00:22:26.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000518
00:22:26.720 --> 00:22:29.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Next time Kaede would like
to come in the daytime.</b></Default>

c0000519
00:22:29.430 --> 00:22:31.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Now that you've conquered
school at nighttime,</b></Default>

c0000520
00:22:31.180 --> 00:22:32.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that should be a breeze for you.</b></Default>

c0000521
00:22:33.940 --> 00:22:36.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That means as of tonight every
single goal in the notebook</b></Default>

c0000522
00:22:36.610 --> 00:22:38.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can be circled.
- Ah.</b></Default>

c0000523
00:22:38.360 --> 00:22:39.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've done that many already?</b></Default>

c0000524
00:22:39.570 --> 00:22:41.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Panda, pudding,
and school were</b></Default>

c0000525
00:22:41.240 --> 00:22:42.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the last ones left to complete!</b></Default>

c0000526
00:22:42.740 --> 00:22:44.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That means we have
to celebrate, huh?</b></Default>

c0000527
00:22:44.490 --> 00:22:48.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes! Oh, but school probably
only gets a triangle so far.</b></Default>

c0000528
00:22:48.450 --> 00:22:49.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think you're okay
to circle it.</b></Default>

c0000529
00:22:50.080 --> 00:22:52.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It has to be after coming
to school during the day.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:22:52.370 --> 00:22:53.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.</b></Default>

c0000531
00:22:53.960 --> 00:22:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But now it feels like
it's really within reach.</b></Default>

c0000532
00:22:56.330 --> 00:22:58.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede's confident tomorrow
she'll be able to make it</b></Default>

c0000533
00:22:58.840 --> 00:23:00.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to school during the day.
- There's no doubt.</b></Default>

c0000534
00:23:01.050 --> 00:23:02.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Tomorrow's gonna be great!</b></Default>

c0000535
00:23:03.220 --> 00:23:04.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just can't wait for tomorrow!</b></Default>

c0000536
00:23:10.720 --> 00:23:12.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede, it's time
to get up.</b></Default>

c0000537
00:23:12.600 --> 00:23:13.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you still asleep?</b></Default>

c0000538
00:23:14.060 --> 00:23:17.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groaning]</b></Default>

c0000539
00:23:18.400 --> 00:23:19.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000540
00:23:21.150 --> 00:23:23.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, morning, big brother.</b></Default>

c0000541
00:23:23.570 --> 00:23:26.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? You are my big brother,
right?</b></Default>

c0000542
00:23:26.780 --> 00:23:28.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000543
00:23:28.160 --> 00:23:30.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah, my legs are sore.</b></Default>

c0000544
00:23:30.330 --> 00:23:32.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You did run around a lot
at the zoo yesterday.</b></Default>

c0000545
00:23:32.410 --> 00:23:34.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The zoo?
I didn't go, though.</b></Default>

c0000546
00:23:34.870 --> 00:23:36.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong with you,
big brother?</b></Default>

c0000547
00:23:37.420 --> 00:23:38.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000548
00:23:39.000 --> 00:23:40.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you--
- Hold on.</b></Default>

c0000549
00:23:40.710 --> 00:23:42.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was my room always
like this or...</b></Default>

c0000550
00:23:43.510 --> 00:23:45.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you--
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000551
00:23:45.300 --> 00:23:47.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Really Kaede?</b></Default>

c0000552
00:23:47.890 --> 00:23:49.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, no duh.</b></Default>

c0000553
00:23:49.720 --> 00:23:52.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Geez, big brother.
What are you talking about?</b></Default>

c0000554
00:23:52.510 --> 00:23:54.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [shudders]</b></Default>

c0000555
00:23:55.680 --> 00:23:58.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000556
00:23:58.730 --> 00:24:01.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>["Fukashigi no Carte" plays]</b></Default>

c0000557
00:24:01.650 --> 00:24:08.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000558
00:24:47.360 --> 00:24:54.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000559
00:24:55.830 --> 00:25:01.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, big brother.
You're such a rascal.</b></Default>

